{"tid":2145052,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"湯文亮：美國實施人權法，我將個file吞落肚","createTime":"2020-08-08T00:16:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T01:14:57.000Z","uid":64603,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f98f3c116d7c14773727c0e0e11b7ae10d9ae33f","tid":2145052,"uid":64603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T00:16:34.000Z","msg":"美國幾時會用人權法制裁香港人<br />\n <br />\n湯文亮博士<br />\n紀惠集團行政總裁<br />\n2020年3月11日<br />\n　　昨日寫了一篇文章關於美國對香港實施人權法，我話美國在貿易戰已經贏了，沒有必要實施人權法。有網友問我夠唔夠膽，如果美國在半年內實施人權法，我將個file吞落肚。沒有問題，不過，如果美國在半年內不實施人權法，我又得到什麼。我要求很簡單，如果美國在2020年9月10日不實施人權法對付任何香港人，社運人士是否可以停止勇武。我相信他們不敢應承，或者，他們各自為戰，不敢替其他人應承。老實說，人權法，美國連提也不敢提。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0zPJVGG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0zPJVGG.jpg&h=5bfea29c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.property.hk/article_content.php?author=PHK_TML2&amp;id=71123&amp;backlist=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.property.hk%2Farticle_content.php%3Fauthor%3DPHK_TML2%26id%3D71123%26backlist%3D1&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDAEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=dc383492\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.property.hk/article_content.php?author=PHK_TML2&amp;id=71123&amp;backlist=1</a>"},{"pid":"770c7d7f5f9fdcf388b06741a2df167600fa5269","tid":2145052,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T00:16:54.000Z","msg":"除咗制裁，今日係梓樂離開9個月<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2144688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2144688</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccyVKr4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccyVKr4.png&h=fbc64625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5tWka9x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5tWka9x.png&h=850fb110&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36f80eb600ef6e5486972d3f372532c350140434","tid":2145052,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"r